title: Statement by the Press Secretary on H.R. 366 | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House
Office of the Press Secretary


For Immediate Release
January 31, 2011

 



Statement by the Press Secretary on H.R. 366





On Monday, January 31, 2011, the President signed into law:

	H.R. 366, which extends the authorization of certain Small Business Administration programs until May 31, 2011.
